# Milestone Tracker

## Master's (2 years)
- Month 1-2: Literature review
- Month 4: Proposal defense ← GATE 1
- Month 7-14: Main experiments
- Month 10: Conference submission ← GATE 2
- Month 17: Draft to advisor ← GATE 3
- Month 23: THESIS DEFENSE ← GATE 4

## Progress Check Template
| Milestone | Target | Status | Notes |
Use: on track / slightly behind / significantly behind

## Committee Meeting 1-Pager
Since last meeting: [done] | Current work: [...] | Results: [...] | Challenges: [...] | Plan to next: [deliverables + dates]

## When Behind
Stuck >3mo with no results → talk to advisor immediately
Paper rejected twice → assess root cause, consider journal
Writing blocked → 2hr/day minimum, show weekly
